"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/oE5KDmMuPNrd4kQBrY48I.png?height=584&width=1517)\\n\\n## About\\n\\nThe journey of a Mundo Lingo Manager starts here. We‚Äôre all here to support you and work together on future projects.\\n\\nNot already in **The Incubator?** You should first join [Mundo Lingo Collaborators](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/onyNgQAi-2VKGNTDGYK9vf20AK-k7i-3qot58G4Qo54) and then apply to be a **Manager** here:\\n\\n[https://form.typeform.com/to/G1bjAQ?typeform-source=mundolingo.org](https://form.typeform.com/to/G1bjAQ?typeform-source=mundolingo.org)\\n\\n## Communication\\n\\nCommunication is **key** to making friends!\\nCheck out our community [guide on Communication](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/QqxhcUkKracAP2iHqr0dOFiVCDuQiSiAVcEGSv_xD7E) before you begin.\\n\\n## üëã Introduce yourself\\n\\nIntroduce yourself to the Incubator group. This is a **must**. Be noticed - Light up the sky üåü, don‚Äôt let anyone not-notice you arrived ‚ú®\\n\\n* Who are you?\\n* What are your passions, hobbies, interests?\\n* How did you get here?\\n* Why are you here?\\n* What are you interested in?\\n* Who are you interested in connecting with?\\n* What skills -if any- can you offer to other members?\\n\\n## Participate and Learn\\n\\n### Use the EOM\\n\\nThe [Events Operations Manual (EOM)](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/QhvLl3HKyYJ2Z1TVX-rwDjVhwLhwX-QNyRHawRUYZFE) aims to collect all the information you could possibly need to be an amazing Manager. Please read it carefully, raise questions about it in the Incubator group if you have any.\\n\\n### Scrums\\n\\n‚è∞ **Weekly**, alternating between **Friday 12AM and Tuesday 12PM GMT** Let‚Äôs get to know each other! Scrums are our time to speak face to face, listen to each other, learn about each others progress and try to answer questions others may have.\\n\\n### Ask for help\\n\\nWe‚Äôre here to help. Ask questions, don‚Äôt suffer in silence!\\n\\n### Use Google\\n\\nDon‚Äôt be that guy/gal who asks *‚Äúwhat does the flag for Iran look like?‚Äù.* If you do, you‚Äôll probably get what you deserve :)\\n\\n### Help Others, Be Supportive.\\n\\nGreat ways to raise your presence in the group\\n\\n* Have a go at answering peoples questions\\n* Even if you don‚Äôt know, support them, if they asked a good question let them know *‚Äòhey that‚Äôs a great question‚Äô!*\\n* Give new members a warm welcome. Reply to them with your personal intro.\\n\\n### Presence Level\\n\\nNobody is checking on you, only you. Be conscious of your own presence level, if it‚Äôs high you will find many friends to help you in your time of need. If to the contrary, it can begin to feel intimidating to speak.\\n\\n![Harold wasn't very present](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/xZ-F3febC12gi6Dr0KMNH.png?height=395&width=1172)\\n\\n## Roadmap Overview\\n\\nSo you‚Äôre wondering when to start and what to to. Here‚Äôs a birds eye view of the road ahead for incoming Managers.\\n\\n1. Venue Investigation\\n2. Receive Flags\\n3. Confirm Venue\\n4. Confirm Team\\n5. Pass Speech Test\\n6. Marketing Setup\\n7. Launch\\n\\n## Help the next generation\\n\\nNew Managers come in all the time and face the same struggles that are now behind you. How could your experience have been easier, and how can we apply that to newbies?\\n\\nWays you can help:\\n\\n* Make suggestions to amend current guides ***\\\\[link needed\\\\]***\\n* Write a guide covering a subject not yet covered ***\\\\[link needed\\\\]***\\n* Volunteer to lead a working group ***\\\\[link needed\\\\]***\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2-XV4fhLg6NN1e0CXAJEl.png?height=300&width=1150)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637832440,\"title\":\"The Incubator\"},\"digest\":\"d0G1l4xvY71ICdSWEDTcDwpOqiYA3hiUQT546ZJ2vy4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"F8zG1zTeZMDpV2_EIlWrsKpmnGDh3SxjOF71ivpgrJg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cTaiHvTF70f6CzGg3oqJ4Z5azdotT-0kGnHltBTC7IE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"IWG72g1ENumwahJZDgoDGegVTLIu5LthPM6-LTV8xITkXxCPSaRStbA7xwHqSbapLuq9qNCOSndl4bs92W4pDg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9ffe03abbb74481883195e9c49f74ad3362bbcc9be4787bc7d86b31ee0a27a51494508e5274ca44c64dfc0a67507f0b6354439a75b1d7c337ff95a9f16a6c4c11b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"F8zG1zTeZMDpV2_EIlWrsKpmnGDh3SxjOF71ivpgrJg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cTaiHvTF70f6CzGg3oqJ4Z5azdotT-0kGnHltBTC7IE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"u9k391Q69s4h51bqyDa5GDeG7HurDVXaOuhFcHcb-Jc\"}"